Hi Trish, 

I had a look into this this. Sometimes when you have already tried to do a post like below, your account/browser caches the result. Facebook is infamous for doing this too. 

Here is a link to LinkedIn's tool that forces a refresh and also shows you what your post will look like: 
https://www.linkedin.com/post-inspector/inspect/https:%2F%2Fmsra.org.au%2F

I have also attached a screenshot for your reference. 

You should be good to go now, but do let me know if you need any further help with this? 

Hope you are well and speak soon,
